                    <span>This is a very good book, especially for the money. It is what it claims to be, "A Beginner's Guide." Don't look here for advanced javascript (only the last chapter deals with that). I bought this book with little understanding of Javascript. After reading this book, I have the foundational skills I need write Javascript. Highly recommended!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">For those without experience this is a great start.</div>
